reviewText:
the dvd had the following episodes....
attack of the jack 0 lanterns- was really good
vampire breathe- was amazing
let's get invisable- was really good
the headless ghost- was ok
awesome ants- was creepy with the bugs and an ok episode
teacher's pet- was ok
scarecrow walks at midnight- was really good
don't go to sleep - was kind of weird
calling all creeps- was a little weird but still good
great price for the 3 pack. highly recommended to any are you afraid of the dark fans or anyone who wants a scare.

i wished they would of came out with this when i first started buying goosebumps dvds, would of saved me some money. this contains 3 disc with 9 eps. the eps r by order of disc Attack of the Jack O'Lanterns, Vampire Breath, Let's Get Invisible, The Headless Ghost, Teacher's Pet, Awesome Ants, The Scarecrow Walks At Midnight,  Don't Go To Sleep! & Calling All Creeps
Awesome for the price! This is not only 3 stories, it's 9!
Great fun. Evocative of childhood ghost stories. Good for Halloween or any time. Not too scary and no gore or swearing.
Was a success for my grand daughters Halloween Party.  The kids loved watching these movies on the big screen outside with pizza and popcorn
Item came just as described and in proper packaging. My child has enjoyed many times over! :)
Great chills and thrills.scary episodes r.l .Stine a genius .
